SAP doesn&#39;t allowed redistribution of ngdbc.jar in their TC as mentioned [here](https://archive.sap.com/discussions/thread/3944326). So you won&#39;t find any legal one online. 

Your only option is to [include the jar from your local](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/4955635/how-to-add-local-jar-files-in-maven-project). Something like:

    &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;sample&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;com.sample&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;version&gt;1.0&lt;/version&gt;
        &lt;scope&gt;system&lt;/scope&gt;
        &lt;systemPath&gt;${project.basedir}/src/main/resources/yourJar.jar&lt;/systemPath&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;

